    <innerclass refid="class_time_manager" prot="public">TimeManager</innerclass>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Real-time clock and time synchronization management. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="author"><para>Claude Code Session 20250720_221011 </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="date"><para>2025-01-20</para>
</simplesect>
Manages system time using DS3231 RTC with NTP synchronization support. Provides timezone handling, alarms, and time formatting capabilities.</para>
<sect1 id="_time_manager_8cpp_1dependencies">
<title>Dependencies</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>RTClib for DS3231 RTC interface</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>NTPClient for network time synchronization</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>WiFi libraries for NTP connectivity</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>ArduinoJson for JSON output</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="_time_manager_8cpp_1hardware">
<title>Hardware Requirements</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>DS3231 RTC module on I2C bus</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>WiFi connectivity for NTP synchronization</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Default I2C pins: SDA=21, SCL=22 </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
